ry to predict the frequency and\npolarization of the lowest frequency antiferromagnetic resonance mode and find\nthat the mode is linearly polarized in the (001)-plane with $f = $ 670 GHz.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 7 Jun 2020 16:32:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
