ignificance of $S \\simeq 11$ for HL-LHC and $S \\simeq 290$ for FCC-hh. Finally\nwe provide quantitative predictions for the dilepton invariant mass\ndistributions and lepton separations which help to identify non-standard\nsignals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Jun 2020 14:07:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 20 Sep 2020 07:46:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 27 Apr 2021 11:20:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-01"}
